纺织品、服装与奢侈品</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.9</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">安踏体育</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(02020)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">85.95（2%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">汽车</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.2</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">比亚迪股份－五百</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(02944)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">110（0%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">资讯科技硬件与设备</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.2</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">小米集团－Ｗ</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(01810)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">41.6（3.7%）</td></tr></table></div>",
